oftware-r2&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p >; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/25/24185946/vw-rivian-joint-venture-investment-software-r2" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/25/24185946/vw-rivian-joint-venture-investment-software-r2</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry></feed>